HEADWORD: Netting
<hw>Net"ting</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Urine.</def> <mark>[Prov.
Eng.]</mark> <rj><au>Halliwell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nettle</ent>⟦br⟧
